  "detailed_description": "<h1>Follow us</h1><p>The new work by Flounder Studios - \"Strive For Power:King Growth Program\"<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001070/extras/5bbe6f54a77b2c45bffcb2584a66de14.avif?t=1772110672\" width=450 height=138 /></span><br>Come join us and immerse yourself in the life of an emperor! Thank you for the support from all the kings. Feel free to follow us, and we will notify everyone as soon as there are updates~ Official Bilibili Channel: @bimoyu Official QQ Groups: 399325180, 626352419</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>The new work by Flounder Studios - \"Strive For Power:King Growth Program\"<br><br>\"Strive For Power:King Growth Program\" is an ancient emperor simulator, in which you will play as a king of the Han Dynasty, using your own strategies and tactics to rule the country and outsmart foreign enemies! With a harem of three thousand beautiful women, including gentle empresses and charming concubines, continuously collect all kinds of beauties!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001070/extras/3b85c06129c785d7ab7297abfe7979ac.avif?t=1772110672\" width=576 height=324 /></span><br><br>★ Game Features ★<br>-Immersive recreation of the life of a Han Dynasty emperor Simulate the real court and the state, attend court sessions to manage the six ministries, gather popular support, and enhance prestige<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001070/extras/d4e04afd3b718cefcaf884e55fd1f56c.poster.avif?t=1772110672\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001070/extras/d4e04afd3b718cefcaf884e55fd1f56c.webm?t=1772110672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001070/extras/d4e04afd3b718cefcaf884e55fd1f56c.mp4?t=1772110672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>-Amidst the crowd, I search for her; I form deep connections with kindred spirits, welcome the beautiful into my life, and encounter thousands of beauties.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001070/extras/917c87ec726593ba1e2826658e25be72.poster.avif?t=1772110672\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001070/extras/917c87ec726593ba1e2826658e25be72.webm?t=1772110672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001070/extras/917c87ec726593ba1e2826658e25be72.mp4?t=1772110672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>-Simulate real palace intrigue Cultivate loyal confidants, capture those with ill intentions, can you discern the ambitions of your officials<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001070/extras/52cbb2f8d6877616d009e5b5a2efedb9.poster.avif?t=1772110672\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001070/extras/52cbb2f8d6877616d009e5b5a2efedb9.webm?t=1772110672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001070/extras/52cbb2f8d6877616d009e5b5a2efedb9.mp4?t=1772110672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>-Thrilling battles of wit and courage Train brave armies, defend towns, vie for dominance on the battlefield, ultimately unify the realm<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001070/extras/dec67eb3a85c332c5c1611a6a1e3411f.poster.avif?t=1772110672\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001070/extras/dec67eb3a85c332c5c1611a6a1e3411f.webm?t=1772110672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001070/extras/dec67eb3a85c332c5c1611a6a1e3411f.mp4?t=1772110672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>-Open character customization Open customizable modules, support character and attribute customization, build your ideal empire.<br>*The functionalities are expected to be supported in the first major update after the release. Stay tuned!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001070/extras/57242d22b568e04298084ecf76db878a.poster.avif?t=1772110672\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001070/extras/57242d22b568e04298084ecf76db878a.webm?t=1772110672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001070/extras/57242d22b568e04298084ecf76db878a.mp4?t=1772110672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
